    {
      "path": "routes/governed-fence-routes.js",
      "register": "registerGovernedFenceRoutes",
      "enabled": true,
      "note": "CONDUCTOR-GLUE separation-of-powers switch. Mounts GET /api/v1/factory/governance/fence + POST .../fence/enable so the SYSTEM can turn its own governance fence ON (GOVERNED_FACTORY_ONLY=1) via Railway API + self-redeploy, but is physically unable to turn it OFF (enable-only ratchet — only a human in Railway can). PR #272 added the guard; this mounts the live surface that was missing so the flip can actually happen. Chair receipt LIFERE_COUNCIL_1783462353983."
