      "mount_path": "/api/v1/accounts",
      "enabled": true,
      "note": "Managed accounts vault + recipe signups at /api/v1/accounts/* on founder lane."
    },
    {
      "path": "routes/marketing-session-routes.js",
      "register": "registerMarketingSessionRoutes",
      "enabled": true,
      "note": "MarketingOS SocialMediaOS Phase 1 JSON API (§6). The autonomous loop rebuilds this file (re-queued mos-session-routes); once deployed the boot mounts it here and the functional-proof gate verifies /api/v1/marketing/* is LIVE before the step can be done. Records a benign 'module not found' health error until the loop ships the file — fail-open, never blocks boot."
